sentences: Marcia Judith Citron (born 1945) is an American professor of musicology at Rice University in Houston, Texas.
Marcia Citron graduated from Brooklyn College with a BA in 1966 and from University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill with an MA in 1968 and a PhD in 1971.
